# events

**Instance Property**

The events in the movie error log.

## Declaration

```swift
var events: [Any]! { get }
```

## Discussion

An ordered collection of [doc://com.apple.mediaplayer/documentation/MediaPlayer/MPMovieErrorLogEvent] instances that represent the chronological sequence of events in the movie error log.

## Movie error log properties

- **extendedLogData**: A textual version of the web server error log.
- **extendedLogDataStringEncoding**: The string encoding for the extended log data property.
